title: Best of: Daniel Ennis
description: Our podcast team is taking a break this week for the holidays. We’re revisiting some of our favorite interviews from 2016.   Daniel Ennis is former director of the NSA Threat Operations Center, or NTOC, and is currently executive director of the University of Maryland Global Initiative on Cyber. We spoke with Daniel Ennis back in July.

content:encoded:
Our podcast team is taking a break this week for the holidays. We’re revisiting some of our favorite interviews from 2016.  
 
Daniel Ennis is former director of the NSA Threat Operations Center, or NTOC, and is currently executive director of the University of Maryland Global Initiative on Cyber. We spoke with Daniel Ennis back in July.
